name: HBC End to end - Place Order Registered/Guest users using Amex Card

elements.name: SFDEV-3310 Verify for Bay website order for a registered user, multiple items multiple quantities, shipment paid by Amex.

steps.name: I login to the application with valid credentials
Remove saved addresses from my account page
Remove saved credit cards from my account page
I click on "checkout button in cart page"
I enter my "Shipping address-SFDEV-3310" in the textbox
I click on - "checkout save shipping address button"
I click on - "checkout shipping save and continue button"
I enter my "Amex Card Details" in the textbox
I click on - "checkout payment section save and continue button"
